-- Nomura: Fired employee at centre of insider probe
-- 
-- Tue Apr 22, 2008 6:43am EDT
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2008/04/22/us-nomura-fired-idUSTKF00310520080422

 

 TOKYO  (Reuters) - Nomura Holdings ( 8604.T ), Japan's largest brokerage house, said on Tuesday it had fired an employee at the centre of an insider trading probe. 

 Nomura said earlier that it faced a probe that sources said involved leaked merger deal information. (Reporting by  Junko Fujita )